# --- SAFETY: never commit real credentials ---
**/scripts/staging/creds/
**/multica-auth-creds/
# i18n locale strings are NOT secrets and MUST stay tracked.
# (git has no inline comments — keep the negation pattern on its own clean line)
**/auth.json
!**/packages/views/locales/**/auth.json
**/.env.production
**/.env.staging
**/deploy/observability/secrets/*
!**/deploy/observability/secrets/*.example
multica-auth-work/apps/mobile/.env.production
multica-auth-work/apps/mobile/.env.staging

